{"tid":1173031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過左條例後會唔會錯誤地引渡左梁天琦同黃之峰返大陸？","createTime":"2019-05-26T23:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T04:07:15.000Z","uid":10320,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4487cc6f848134b921901674535fa374b0220882","tid":1173031,"uid":10320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T23:39:00.000Z","msg":"錯誤地無審訊就引渡返大陸打靶？ <br />\n<br />\n懲教錯誤地送左人上去後， 公安又錯誤地以為係死刑犯<br />\n<br />\n跟住港警察又錯誤地提供資料， 或錯誤地聯絡錯既公安分局<br />\n<br />\n公安就錯誤地冇人聯絡之下就處死左兩人<br />\n<br />\n公報左之後先發現原來搞錯左好多野？ <br />\n<br />\n政府之後對事件表示遺憾， 並表示將來會再嚴格審查所有引渡項目？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31363e7686b956d87e20cf2ef640e8740979684","tid":1173031,"uid":245484,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T23:48:20.000Z","msg":"死就死撚緊嫁喇<br />\n不過應該唔會係第一波<br />\n中共而家首要既係捉有錢佬返去補血"},{"pid":"0cc9e3287797e5640aa921f2fda529062534a78b","tid":1173031,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:13:48.000Z","msg":"君臨天下大量放售"},{"pid":"203beb91eb7fa2778b5803b6b94dd24ae0dc829f","tid":1173031,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:29:53.000Z","msg":"不嬲錯唔錯都有糧出"},{"pid":"908c6bcdb21a5a9ad2237f1fa259513cb29a7faa","tid":1173031,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}